/* eslint-disable no-unused-vars */ /* eslint-disable react/prop-types */ import { Avatar, Box, Badge, Card, CardContent, Grid, Table, TableRow, TableCell, Typography, TableBody, TableContainer, Paper, TableHead, } from "@mui/material"; import PrecisionManufacturingIcon from "@mui/icons-material/PrecisionManufacturing"; import PropTypes from "prop-types"; export const Machine = (props) => { const { machineId, moldId, monaNumber, status, moldShots, failedShots, prodRate, prod_startDate, prod_startTime, prod_endDate, prod_endTime, material, moldMaker, ...others } = props; return ( {/* machine id */} Machine {machineId} {/* mona number */} Mona Number {monaNumber} {/* statics table */} {/* statistics */} Molds Mold Shots {moldShots} Failed Shots {failedShots} Production Hourly Rate {prodRate} Mold Maker {moldMaker} Material {material} Mold ID {moldId} {/* Start Date {prod_startDate} Start Time {prod_startTime} End Date {prod_endDate} */} {/* End Time {prod_endTime} */}
); }; Machine.propTypes = { machineId: PropTypes.string.isRequired, monaNumber: PropTypes.string.isRequired, status: PropTypes.string, };
